      "value": "<p>You’ve trained in how to take your foes alive.</p><hr /><p><strong>Benefit:</strong> When you attempt to deal nonlethal damage with a lethal melee weapon, you take a –2 penalty instead of the standard –4 penalty on your attack roll. Starting at 5th level you take no penalty. If you’re using a weapon that already deals nonlethal damage, deal 2 bonus damage.</p>"
